{"tid":2031604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[同志们快Backup] 百度百科条目：「民族自强」","createTime":"2020-05-23T13:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T13:45:03.000Z","uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"03a801958f524683adf40b96d42414f47571486a","tid":2031604,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:34:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民族自強</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n民族自強，是指一個民族建立<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>在自尊、自信基礎上的依靠自身力量</strong></span>實現民族振興和國家富強的英雄氣概和創造精神。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nTvMjQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nTvMjQ.jpg&h=9cb1c55e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這種自強是一個民族在認識其自身存在和發展的狀況、處境、<strong>特別是與其他民族國家的差距之後</strong>，形成的一種<strong>責任意識和進取精神</strong>，是一種任何時候都<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">不願做別國附庸 、獨立自主地</span></ins></span>解決自己國家的問題的民族精神。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CbgAXqU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCbgAXqU.jpg&h=1d18a6c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9d39238c2819d78d0838f037609f5af00eb003","tid":2031604,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXH08z2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXH08z2.jpg&h=d0a16b0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12109ed3ff9524b29da4985bcbb6674969d191ca","tid":2031604,"uid":273133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:37:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">民族自強<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">ONE Nation<br />\nONE Hong Kong</span></strong><br />\n香港獨立</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"5ffbef8ec2ff64c769919a47cfb2ac088b29a3cf","tid":2031604,"uid":273133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c9d39238c2819d78d0838f037609f5af00eb003","tid":2031604,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXH08z2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXH08z2.jpg&h=d0a16b0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:37:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">民族自強<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">ONE Nation<br />\nONE Hong Kong</span></strong><br />\n香港獨立</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"3a2d7d27ac2fc89b6395260ca022fe65be662831","tid":2031604,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:38:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">ONE NATION<br />\nONE HONG KONG</div></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1630296f018857b81605cb96d6645838d4f1542e","tid":2031604,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:41:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">One Nation<br />\nOne Hong Kong</span></div></strong></span>"},{"pid":"99d1d27e573bb149c770a1356912d0377aee91c4","tid":2031604,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:44:08.000Z","msg":"西門巴打萬事小心保重。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9084d15e43508e9a6913acf1ae0c39d38f486f62","tid":2031604,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:44:31.000Z","msg":"丟掉幻想, 大把和理非驚死 + 黑警戒嚴, 講大遊行果D只係一廂情願<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳[巴士人鏈]<br />\n限聚令豁免排隊, 黑警分唔到你係咪真排隊搭巴士<br />\n主力部隊集中去頭站, 只要頭站架架車滿載, 中途站上唔到車就可以排隊組人鏈<br />\n排到累去黃店抖吓, 差完電再排過<br />\n畫面夠靚, 岩哂和理非, 有機會上到國際頭版<br />\n<br />\n時間無多, 認同請推post及分享給身邊黃絲朋友<br />\n<br />\nbriefing:<br />\n聽日呢, 9成9人都係行街架啦, 黑警好快就搞亂個場, 俾人驅散後就嘗試叫大家5x聚人, 坐爆5x車, 企爆5x站, 祝大家平安回家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2030973/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2030973/page/1?post=1</a>"},{"pid":"9f933c29d9f2eb34d1e5f0c308523fc71e82e3d4","tid":2031604,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1032d55238a8201189a2f558277a7975197a328d","tid":2031604,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99d1d27e573bb149c770a1356912d0377aee91c4","tid":2031604,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:44:08.000Z","msg":"西門巴打萬事小心保重。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家咁話"}]}